    <title></title>
    <link href="/2022/10/04/%E3%80%8AIDENTITY-SENSITIVE%20KNOWLEDGE%20PROPAGATION%20FOR%20CLOTH-CHANGING%20PERSON%20RE-IDENTIFICATION%E3%80%8B/"/>
    <url>/2022/10/04/%E3%80%8AIDENTITY-SENSITIVE%20KNOWLEDGE%20PROPAGATION%20FOR%20CLOTH-CHANGING%20PERSON%20RE-IDENTIFICATION%E3%80%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="《IDENTITY-SENSITIVE-KNOWLEDGE-PROPAGATION-FOR-CLOTH-CHANGING-PERSON-RE-IDENTIFICATION》"><a href="#《IDENTITY-SENSITIVE-KNOWLEDGE-PROPAGATION-FOR-CLOTH-CHANGING-PERSON-RE-IDENTIFICATION》" class="headerlink" title="《IDENTITY-SENSITIVE KNOWLEDGE PROPAGATION FOR CLOTH-CHANGING PERSON RE-IDENTIFICATION》"></a>《IDENTITY-SENSITIVE KNOWLEDGE PROPAGATION FOR CLOTH-CHANGING PERSON RE-IDENTIFICATION》</h3><h4 id="1-摘要简介"><a href="#1-摘要简介" class="headerlink" title="1.摘要简介"></a>1.摘要简介</h4><p>  目前，典型的基于生物识别的换衣行人重识别方法往往需要繁琐的姿势或身体部位估计器来学习与衣服不相关的的特征，这带来了很高的计算成本。此外，由于监控图像的分辨率下降，性能受到很大限制。为了解决上述限制，本文提出了一个有效的身份敏感的信息传播框架(DeSKPro) 用于换衣行人重识别。通过从人体解析模块获取信息引入了一个与衣服不相关的空间注意力模块，以消除服装外观的干扰；人同时为了缓解分辨率下降的问题问题，并从人脸中挖掘身份敏感的线索，本文使用已有的面部信息来恢复丢失的面部细节，然后传播到一个较小的网络获取面部特征。</p><h4 id="2-结构"><a href="#2-结构" class="headerlink" title="2.结构"></a>2.结构</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004153039005.png" alt="image-20221004153039005"></p><h4 id="3-具体方法"><a href="#3-具体方法" class="headerlink" title="3.具体方法"></a>3.具体方法</h4><ul><li><strong>1.Mask-Guided Cloth-irrelevant Feature Stream</strong></li></ul><blockquote><ul><li>结构</li></ul></blockquote><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004153425625.png" alt="image-20221004153425625"></p><blockquote><ul><li><p>OSNet Block &lt;<Omni-Scale Feature Learning for Person Re-Identification>&gt;</p><p>文章提出了全尺度(omni-scale)学习的概念，并就此提出了全尺度学习的网络OSNet，来解决ReID中需要关注不同尺度特征流的问题</p><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004161500102.png" alt="image-20221004161500102"></p></li></ul></blockquote><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004154121462.png" alt="image-20221004154121462"></p><blockquote><ul><li>MBN</li></ul><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004154433586.png" alt="image-20221004154433586"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004155155093.png" alt="image-20221004155155093"></p><ul><li>L_attn</li></ul></blockquote><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004153820445.png" alt="image-20221004153820445"></p><ul><li><strong>2.Facial Feature Enhancement Stream</strong></li></ul><blockquote><ul><li>结构</li></ul><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004155742099.png" alt="image-20221004155742099"></p><ul><li>L_fkp</li></ul><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004160320392.png" alt="image-20221004160320392"></p></blockquote><h4 id="4-损失函数"><a href="#4-损失函数" class="headerlink" title="4.损失函数"></a>4.损失函数</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004160408226.png" alt="image-20221004160408226"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004160421401.png" alt="image-20221004160421401"></p><h4 id="5-实验"><a href="#5-实验" class="headerlink" title="5.实验"></a>5.实验</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004160815903.png" alt="image-20221004160815903"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\26440\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221004160851508.png" alt="image-20221004160851508"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
